reviews.review_text: The last MSG Show Really?? Stranger into Bertha was great. The energy was great even though the band was tired as to be expected after i think eight other shows on this MSG run... May God Rest jerry and all we love and care for with him forever>>>
- Certainly not a bad show for 1994, and there is definitely lots of energy and some highlights, but overall, not a very technically well-played show.
